        init container with the attributes
        Pos: a new container has been created
        Parameters:
        id - as String. id is the identification code unic
        weight - as double. weight is the weight of the container
        type - as char. type is the type of the container. 't' for tank container, 'a' for dryvan 20 or 'b' for dryvan 40
        description - as String. description is what the container have
        input - as boolean. input is if the container is arriving or not
        days - as int. days is the number of days on the port
